    "description": "<p>TECHCOM SOLUTIONS founded in &nbsp;2003 is a Total Solutions Provider in IT sector working with Government agencies, MNCs, System Integrators , Educational Institutions &amp; BFSI. Providing structured services for projects outsourcing, managed services and staffing solutions across skillsets &nbsp;in Singapore and APAC. &nbsp;Local Singaporean company with an MSC status company in Malaysia and Shared Services centre in India.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are a transactional technology provider with focus on Customised Integrated Solutions, Strategic Outsourcing &amp; Professional Services and Client Communications.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>It is manned by professionals with a proven track record in the industry, combined with technical expertise &amp; dedication. The right platform for aspiring candidates who want to make a mark in IT domain and mid-career PMETs who want to switch &amp; get trained in IT .</p>\n<p><br></p>",
